main_body:
Regulation (EC) No 1433/2003 is hereby amended as follows:
1. the following paragraph is added to Article 17:
2. in Article 26(1), ‘1 June’ is replaced by ‘15 November’;
3. in Annex I, point 2(d) is replaced by:
‘(d) quality improvement measures, including certified mycelium and plants and seed of the categories “basic seed” and “certified seed”, as defined by Council Directive 2002/55/EC (4);
4. in part 3 of Annex III, point 3 is deleted.
